End Process

Process called "hir_get_import_hide" takes node as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Get the hide-combinator name List of a HIR_IMPORT node

    @Implementation:
    HIR_IMPORT property "hide_list" (List of name strings). 0 when the
    import has no hide combinator.
