    @End Implementation

    Return proc hir_set_metadata with node, "is_abstract", is_abstract
End Process

Process called "hir_set_return_type" takes node as Integer, return_type as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Set the declared return type of a callable node

    @Implementation:
