Process called "hir_get_new_arguments" takes node as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Get the argument-collection handle of a HIR_NEW node

    @Implementation:
    The new-expression node owns its argument lists directly, so the
    node itself is the collection handle consumed by
    hir_get_positional_args and hir_get_named_args. Null propagates
    as 0.
    @End Implementation

    Return node
End Process

