    End If

    proc hir_set_metadata with node, "operator", operator
    proc hir_set_metadata with node, "operand", operand

    Return node
End Process

Process called "hir_create_ternary_expr" takes condition as Integer, then_expr as Integer, else_expr as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Create a HIR_TERNARY_EXPR expression node

    @Implementation:
