Process called "hir_create_new" takes type_name as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Create a HIR_NEW instantiation expression node

    @Implementation:
    Standard HIRNode of kind HIR_NEW with property "type_name" (string,
    possibly carrying a named-constructor suffix; the key
    hir_get_new_type_name reads) set at construction. The node itself is
    the argument-collection handle (hir_get_new_arguments returns it).
    Returns 0 on allocation failure.
    @End Implementation

