    Note: Get the return type of a HIR_FUNCTION_TYPE node

    @Implementation:
    HIR_FUNCTION_TYPE property "return_type" (type node) - the same key
    as the callable declarations for producer uniformity.
    @End Implementation

    Return proc hir_get_metadata with node, "return_type"
